text: Islanovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Karacha-Yelginsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 56 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 26 km from Kushnarenkovo, 5 km from Karacha-Yelga. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Islanovo
